The milestone also means the cableway has had a million visitors in just 11 months a record.The 25-millionth visitor Bafana Sibanyoni rode to the top of Table Mountain in February 2015. Wednesday s 26-millionth tourist was Elbe Mattheus from Cradock in the Eastern Cape.She won free tickets for her and boyfriend Morne Viljoen a Monopoly Cape Town game a spa treatment and afternoon tea for two at a Cape Town hotel.Cableway managing director Wahida Parker said it had taken 28 years for the cableway to record its first-millionth visitor in 1957. But thanks to a bumper number of visitors during August September and October 2016 and an exceptional festive season the cableway reached the latest million visits in just 11 months she said.- TMG Digital/The Times